<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>KYC Submission - WealthWise</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #eef2f7;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 30px;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 650px;
      background: #ffffff;
      padding: 25px 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 14px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      margin: auto;
      border-top: 5px solid #0056b3;
    }
    h2 {
      color: #0056b3;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      font-size: 22px;
    }
    p {
      color: #444;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 8px 0;
    }
    .kyc-status {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #ff9800;
    }
    .highlight {
      color: #0056b3;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 25px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #777;
      border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding-top: 12px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>New KYC Submission</h2>
    <p>Hello <span class="highlight">WealthWise Admin</span>,</p>
    
    <p>A new KYC document has been submitted by <strong>{{name}}</strong> for verification.</p>
    <p><strong>KYC Status:</strong> <span class="kyc-status">Pending Review</span></p>
    
    <p>Kindly log in to your WealthWise dashboard to review and either <span class="highlight">Approve</span> or <span class="highlight">Reject</span> the submission.</p>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Best regards,<br>ðŸ’¼ WealthWise Compliance Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
